nodes.text: TK-511 was a stormtrooper of the Galactic Empire.
In 1 ABY TK-511 was part of a stormtrooper unit that guarded a statue of Emperor Palpatine installed in front of the Theed Royal Palace on Naboo during that year's Empire Day celebrations.
TK-511 was a Non-Player Character (NPC) in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. He made appearances during the annual Empire Day live events of 2008 to 2011.
